179
00:14:21,444 --> 00:14:23,862
The man from Cunard says
we're to be at the dock an hour early.

180
00:14:24,030 --> 00:14:25,656
We'll meet here, and then go to...

181
00:14:25,740 --> 00:14:27,115
God damn it!

