192
00:15:14,956 --> 00:15:17,666
Well, you do like your little games, don't you?

193
00:15:19,419 --> 00:15:20,752
You seem to enjoy them yourself.

194
00:15:21,879 --> 00:15:23,505
Very wicked, my love.

195
00:15:39,522 --> 00:15:40,856
