226
00:17:13,533 --> 00:17:15,784
To get back the money you lifted from him.

227
00:17:16,452 --> 00:17:18,245
I worked my tail off for it.

228
00:17:20,915 --> 00:17:22,457
My little girl.

229
00:17:25,461 --> 00:17:27,838
